import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import {AiOutlineCamera} from 'react-icons/ai' const Cards = () => { const [cameraNotWorking, setCameraNotWorking] = useState({ cam1: 0, cam2: 0, cam3: 0, cam4: 0 }); useEffect(() => { fetch('http://localhost:8000/CameraNotWorking') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setCameraNotWorking({ cam1: data.cam1_count, cam2: data.cam2_count, cam3: data.cam3_count, cam4: data.cam4_count }); }) .catch(error => console.error('Error fetching number of offline sites:', error)); }, []); return (
